Calculate pairwise RMSD for trajectory and plot¶

In [1]:
import pytraj as pt
from pytraj.plot import plot_matrix
In [2]:
traj = pt.iterload("tz2.nc", "tz2.parm7")
In [3]:
mat = pt.pairwise_rmsd(traj, '@CA')
